# API Design

## Authentication
POST /auth/login  
GET  /auth/me  

## Users
GET /users/me  
GET /users (admin)  
GET /users/birthdays (admin)

## Events
GET /events  
POST /events (admin)  
GET /events/{id}  
PUT /events/{id} (admin)  
DELETE /events/{id} (admin)

## Registrations
POST /events/{id}/register  
GET /events/{id}/registrations (admin)  
DELETE /registrations/{id}
